# Template file for 'orchis-gtk-theme'
pkgname=orchis-gtk-theme
_yy=2025
_mm=04
_dd=25
version=${_yy}.${_mm}.${_dd}
revision=1
#archs="i686 x86_64"
#build_wrksrc=
#conf_files=""
#make_dirs="/var/log/dir 0755 root root"
hostmakedepends="gzip tar gtk-update-icon-cache sassc"
makedepends=""
depends="gtk-engine-murrine gnome-themes-extra gnome-themes-extra-gtk sassc"
short_desc="A modern style rounded theme for gnome and gtk applications"
maintainer="alfejz <alfredoejz@mailo.com>"
license="GPL-3.0-or-later"
homepage="https://github.com/vinceliuice/Orchis-theme"
changelog="https://github.com/vinceliuice/Orchis-theme/releases"
distfiles="https://github.com/vinceliuice/Orchis-theme/archive/refs/tags/${_yy}-${_mm}-${_dd}.tar.gz"
checksum=d479653415e271fe9f3324f1f4f51cf28b1134164667142c6c6a6db41cf4da9b

noshlibprovides=yes

do_extract() {
    cd ${wrksrc}
    cp "${XBPS_SRCDISTDIR}/${pkgname}-${version}/${_yy}-${_mm}-${_dd}.tar.gz" "${wrksrc}/"
    tar -xzvf "${wrksrc}/${_yy}-${_mm}-${_dd}.tar.gz" "Orchis-theme-${_yy}-${_mm}-${_dd}/" \
        --strip-components=1
}

do_install() {
    vmkdir /usr/share/themes 755
    ${wrksrc}/install.sh -d "${DESTDIR}/usr/share/themes" --tweaks macos
}
